    "CMV_neurologic_disease": {
      "text": "Ganciclovir\n5mg/kg IV q12hrs daily x 21 days FOLLOWED BY 5mg/kg IV q24hrs +\nFoscarnet\n90mg/kg IV q12hrs x 21 days THEN 90-120mg/kg IV q24hrs",
